{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to go through to the-- to the colonel's, room who was the-- then the chief there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in a few minutes, the interrogator who interrogated me right at that moment, that captain just pushed me in the corner.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the excitement, they just forgot about me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Completely forget about me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They got so, so, so scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I overheard some things that-- that this Rose was talking about the Red Army, the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was all oh, oh by God, here is my-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do whatever you want with me, but here's-- here's my-- my salvation, the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Red Army, see?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was there about two hours, running back and forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the time they took me into-- into my cell, and I saw smoke go-- going up and I had to jump to grab the bar and pull, pull myself.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I saw a big pile of papers and papers, all that burning in the-- you know, all the-- all the prison documents, they were burning-- burning up.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought, well, here's the time they nearly-- but it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we spent a-- spent a night-- we were another night there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next day, they put me up with [NON-ENGLISH] the other group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The first, the captain, and another lieutenant, they were-- they were shipped out first into [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a summer resort in the Buda-- in the Buda Hills.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
